Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.16,zh,,0,0,0,,出乎很多人的意料\N{\ren}It came as a shock to many...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.21,0:00:13.67,zh,,0,0,0,,我们的独裁者被无情消灭，在这权力真空之中\N{\ren}But with the power vacuum left by the heartless consumption of our dictator,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:15.87,zh,,0,0,0,,我们要实施更多严苛的饼干法律\N{\ren}we shall impose even more Draconian cookie law,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:17.74,zh,,0,0,0,,一条一条地出炉\N{\ren}one be -cookieing at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:22.52,zh,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\ren}Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:24.79,zh,,0,0,0,,你和你外公离开后它们立马就掌权了\N{\ren}They took power immediately after you and your grandpa left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:29.23,zh,,0,0,0,,真抱歉，瑞克不管权力交接的，他当时应该只是饿了\N{\ren}Err sorry about that, Rick doesn't really do 'transition plans', I -I think he was just hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:32.45,zh,,0,0,0,,那既然你来了，帮我们建立新的体制吧\N{\ren}Well, now with you here, perhaps a new system of government?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:34.62,zh,,0,0,0,,-莫蒂国王 -抱歉，我得闪了\N{\ren}King Morty - -Sorry, look I gotta run,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:35.89,zh,,0,0,0,,你们一定能搞定的\N{\ren}I -I'm sure you guys'll figure it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.11,zh,,0,0,0,,我相信你们\N{\ren}I -I believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:42.98,zh,,0,0,0,,可以帮我们堵住这个UFO形状的洞吗？\N{\ren}Morty! Can you help us with this UFO -shaped hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.55,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，纯粹是因为\N{\ren}Sure, geez, but y'know only because
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:45.77,zh,,0,0,0,,我刚好路过\N{\ren}I was in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:52.08,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，谢天谢地\N{\ren}Morty, thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:54.73,zh,,0,0,0,,你外公离开后，这怪兽就出现了\N{\ren}The beast emerged right after your grandpa left
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:00:58.56,zh,,0,0,0,,-而且它的宝石还不见了 -天啊，真是太巧了\N{\ren}and its gem went missing - -Geez, that is a crazy coincidence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.39,zh,,0,0,0,,我建议最好不要多加探究\N{\ren}that I -I if I were you, probably just best left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:03.39,zh,,0,0,0,,没错，我们应该庆祝一番\N{\ren}He's right. We -We should celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:04.74,zh,,0,0,0,,-要吃顿大餐吗？ -我没空\N{\ren} -Feast? -No time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.78,0:01:06.09,zh,,0,0,0,,听起来很棒\N{\ren}S -S -Sounds pretty classic though,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:07.79,zh,,0,0,0,,你们自己吃吧\N{\ren}don't let me hold you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:13.62,zh,,0,0,0,,王八蛋，他做了记号\N{\ren}Son of a bitch. He marked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:41.82,zh,,0,0,0,,搞什…\N{\ren}What the - -
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:46.83,zh,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\N{\ren}Hey, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:48.31,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\ren}Agh! Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:49.70,zh,,0,0,0,,你也沾到了绿色的东西，对吧？\N{\ren}You got some of that green stuff on you too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:51.48,zh,,0,0,0,,完了，真的完了\N{\ren}Th -Th -This is bad. Th -This is really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:53.27,zh,,0,0,0,,嘿，你觉得我有何感受？\N{\ren}Hey, how do you think I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:56.14,zh,,0,0,0,,我原本有个百宝袋，结果现在大腿上有一个小孩\N{\ren}I had the ultimate stash hole and now I got a kid in my thigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:30.48,zh,,0,0,0,,虽然你感觉是个大好人\N{\ren}Look, you seem like a perfectly nice guy in my hand hole,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:34.00,zh,,0,0,0,,但我若没解决这件事，我就完了\N{\ren}but if I can't sort this out I'm dead - -
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:35.66,zh,,0,0,0,,你搞什么，老兄？好恶\N{\ren}What the hell, dude? Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.75,zh,,0,0,0,,-我只是… -你只是怎样？\N{\ren} -I -I -I was just trying to... -You're just trying to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.31,zh,,0,0,0,,这些是哪来的？\N{\ren}Where'd this stuff come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.32,zh,,0,0,0,,垃圾虫，快出来吃垃圾\N{\ren}Garbage Goober, get out here and eat this garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:44.84,zh,,0,0,0,,垃圾，我好爱垃圾，好吃的垃圾\N{\ren}Mmm, trash, I love trash, yum yum trash,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:47.02,zh,,0,0,0,,-我想吃垃圾 -我超爱它的\N{\ren}I wanna eat trash - -Hell yeah, I love that lil guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.50,zh,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\ren}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:51.02,zh,,0,0,0,,这量子传送液里是加了激浪吗？\N{\ren}Is that Mountain Dew in my quantum transport solution?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.33,zh,,0,0,0,,我看到你做了记号\N{\ren}I -I saw you were marking the levels
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:54.55,zh,,0,0,0,,-只好加满… -加满？\N{\ren} -so I -I had to top it off. -"Top it off?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.68,zh,,0,0,0,,你知道这东西毒性有多强吗？\N{\ren}Do you know how dangerously toxic this stuff is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:58.51,zh,,0,0,0,,你竟然加到我的传送液里？\N{\ren}And you added it to my portal fluid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:00.12,zh,,0,0,0,,因为你不信任我\N{\ren}Only because you don't trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.51,zh,,0,0,0,,逻辑真棒，莫蒂\N{\ren}Oh, that's great logic, Morty - -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.69,zh,,0,0,0,,抱歉我没办法比主厨飞吻的手势\N{\ren}forgive me for not doing the kissy chef gesture
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.34,zh,,0,0,0,,因为你可能把东西洒得到处都是\N{\ren}since you probably spilled this shit everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:06.69,zh,,0,0,0,,我不想把我的嘴唇传送走\N{\ren}and I don't want to teleport my lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:08.26,zh,,0,0,0,,我没洒出来\N{\ren}I did I did not spill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:09.91,zh,,0,0,0,,我不会相信你，我也不该相信你\N{\ren}I won't take your word for that and I shouldn't have to,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:11.61,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我才设了搭档守则\N{\ren}which is why I have sidekick rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.35,zh,,0,0,0,,你如果无法遵守…\N{\ren}If you can't follow them - -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:15.35,zh,,0,0,0,,你就会换掉我，对…你每次都这样说\N{\ren}I can be replaced, yeah, yeah, so you keep telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:17.87,zh,,0,0,0,,抱歉，你觉得我是在吹牛吗？\N{\ren}Excuse me? Did you just try to call my bluff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.22,zh,,0,0,0,,你有看过我吹牛吗？\N{\ren}Have you ever seen me bluff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:20.57,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，你就换掉我好了\N{\ren}Fine. You know what, replace me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.23,zh,,0,0,0,,换掉我，瑞克，快换掉我\N{\ren}Replace me, Rick! Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:23.71,zh,,0,0,0,,希望你能找到\N{\ren}Good luck finding someone that can be told
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:25.36,zh,,0,0,0,,愿意被你威胁换掉八万次的人\N{\ren}80 thousand times how replaceable they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:28.06,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，我决定让你面对现实\N{\ren}Okay. I'll see your bluff call and raise you reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.15,zh,,0,0,0,,我其实还蛮期待这一刻的\N{\ren}I can't pretend I haven't been looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.58,zh,,0,0,0,,这是＂比莫蒂好的事物轮盘＂\N{\ren}Behold my Wheel of Better Things Than Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:35.06,zh,,0,0,0,,你是小孩吗？这是美术劳动课的作业吗？\N{\ren}Wh -What are you eight? I -Is this macaroni art?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.28,zh,,0,0,0,,你觉得这能证明\N{\ren}You expect me to believe you built this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:37.89,zh,,0,0,0,,你不在乎吗？\N{\ren}because you don't care?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.55,zh,,0,0,0,,不，这证明我对你完全没有期望\N{\ren}No, I built this because I don't expect shit from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:40.81,zh,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\ren}Come on, anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:42.25,zh,,0,0,0,,除了莫蒂以外什么都好\N{\ren}Anything but Morty, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:43.55,zh,,0,0,0,,来吧，宝贝，不要归零\N{\ren}Come on baby, no whammies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.99,zh,,0,0,0,,停，好，就这样\N{\ren}Duh -duh -duh -duh stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.47,zh,,0,0,0,,两只乌鸦\N{\ren}Okay, that's it. Two crows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.08,zh,,0,0,0,,你被开除了，知道吗？去吃屎啦\N{\ren}You're fired! You know what? Eat shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.30,zh,,0,0,0,,你只是想让我觉得自己一文不值\N{\ren}You're just trying to make me feel worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:50.91,zh,,0,0,0,,我从没这样说过\N{\ren}I never said you're worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:52.47,zh,,0,0,0,,我其实把你的价值讲得很清楚\N{\ren}In fact, I've given you a very clear metric of your worth:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:53.91,zh,,0,0,0,,两只乌鸦\N{\ren}Two crows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:55.74,zh,,0,0,0,,注意，我可没说三只乌鸦\N{\ren}Note I didn't say three!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:58.61,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，你们的关系好不健康\N{\ren}Man, that is not a healthy relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.57,zh,,0,0,0,,希望你不介意我偷听\N{\ren}I hope you don't mind me eavesdropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:01.83,zh,,0,0,0,,或许我们能想办法\N{\ren}Maybe we can figure out some sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.57,zh,,0,0,0,,贴创可贴隔音\N{\ren}sound -proof bandage solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:05.92,zh,,0,0,0,,垃圾虫有吃掉我的色情杂志吗？\N{\ren}Hey did Garbage Goober eat my porno magazines?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.58,zh,,0,0,0,,你曾是瑞克的朋友吗？\N{\ren}So, were you like, a friend of Rick's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.58,zh,,0,0,0,,-你是吗？ -问得好\N{\ren} -Were you? -Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.58,zh,,0,0,0,,他在干吗？他是不是故意\N{\ren}W -What's he doing, i -is he out there making sure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:13.84,zh,,0,0,0,,要抓两只乌鸦给你看？\N{\ren}you see him collecting two crows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.11,zh,,0,0,0,,你现在心里想着＂天啊, 或许他在意我＂\N{\ren}And now you're thinking, gee, maybe if he cares enough
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.41,zh,,0,0,0,,＂才会想伤我…＂\N{\ren}to hurt me this bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.41,zh,,0,0,0,,...\N{\ren}dot dot dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.68,zh,,0,0,0,,打破这恶性循环吧，莫蒂\N{\ren}Break the cycle, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.94,zh,,0,0,0,,改变你可以改变的事物\N{\ren}Change the things that you can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:27.81,zh,,0,0,0,,我就是这么做的，所以我自由了\N{\ren}That's what I did. And now I'm free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.95,zh,,0,0,0,,我们要把六年的时间缩成六分钟\N{\ren}Only cramming six years into six minutes, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:34.65,zh,,0,0,0,,慢慢来\N{\ren}Take your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:36.13,zh,,0,0,0,,这样就对了\N{\ren}Now that's what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.95,zh,,0,0,0,,你们下次若再成功，我有安眠酮\N{\ren}If ya nail this next one, I've got bird quaaludes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.61,zh,,0,0,0,,我或许会分你们吃\N{\ren}And I might even share.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.31,zh,,0,0,0,,你可以不用再故意刺激我了\N{\ren}Y -You know you can stop doing that for my benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:43.61,zh,,0,0,0,,或者你要继续作秀也没关系，我不干了\N{\ren}Y'know or -or keep doing it. Doesn't matter. I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.96,zh,,0,0,0,,-我要走了 -等等，莫蒂，你先别走\N{\ren} -I'm walking away. -Wait. Morty. Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.88,zh,,0,0,0,,你先看看这个\N{\ren}Not until you see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:50.01,zh,,0,0,0,,开始，鸟之绳索\N{\ren}Commence bird on a wire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:56.62,zh,,0,0,0,,好耶\N{\ren}Yeeeeaaaahhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:59.15,zh,,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\ren}Jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.54,zh,,0,0,0,,喂，我们一起玩吧\N{\ren}Hey, let's hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.54,zh,,0,0,0,,我们是共患难的兄弟\N{\ren}We're like brothers now, we both got away y'know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:03.89,zh,,0,0,0,,你在哪？\N{\ren}w -where are you at?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.24,zh,,0,0,0,,该死，不行\N{\ren}Ooh, you know what, shoot, can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:07.64,zh,,0,0,0,,-我是外星人，所以… -没关系\N{\ren}I'm an alien, um, so - -That's okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.98,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克把我的脚踏车变成太空船\N{\ren}Rick turned my bike into a spaceship
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.64,zh,,0,0,0,,进行单人冒险，让我去帮他拿\N{\ren}for "solo adventures" like picking up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.16,zh,,0,0,0,,金星脚软膏\N{\ren}his Venusian foot ointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.16,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，是我之前太盲目了\N{\ren}God I'm seeing it so clearly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:20.65,zh,,0,0,0,,等等，你的位置是在地球上\N{\ren}Oh. Wait. I -It says here you're on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.82,zh,,0,0,0,,-对，别来这里 -为什么？\N{\ren} -Yeah. Ah. Don't come here. -Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:24.83,zh,,0,0,0,,我懂，我房间有时候也很乱\N{\ren}Look, I -I get it, my room is sometimes messy too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.48,zh,,0,0,0,,我可以去你家门口接…\N{\ren}I'll -I'll pick you up right outside your...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:29.88,zh,,0,0,0,,-精神病院？ -被发现了\N{\ren} -...mental asylum. -Busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.49,zh,,0,0,0,,你刚说你很自由\N{\ren}You literally said "I'm free."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:34.49,zh,,0,0,0,,我并不自由\N{\ren}I'm literally not free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:37.01,zh,,0,0,0,,住手，别拉我的被子\N{\ren}Stop! That's my blanket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.41,zh,,0,0,0,,你怎么会认识瑞克？\N{\ren}How do you know Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.75,zh,,0,0,0,,某天酒吧打烊后\N{\ren}Look I came to your place with him one night
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.06,zh,,0,0,0,,我跟他去你家\N{\ren}after the bar closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.84,zh,,0,0,0,,我在车库里摸东摸西\N{\ren}I started messing around in your garage
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:45.67,zh,,0,0,0,,一不小心就把传送液倒在身上\N{\ren}and I spilled that portal stuff on me and he...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.72,zh,,0,0,0,,然后他就把我传送到了澳洲\N{\ren}kind of launched me to Australia...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:50.20,zh,,0,0,0,,用了莫名原始的弹射器，但弹药是…\N{\ren}like with this weirdly primitive catapult, but - -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.29,zh,,0,0,0,,但弹药是一个气密舱\N{\ren}but the ammunition is an airtight carbon chamber,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.51,zh,,0,0,0,,他也是这样送走有线电视维修员\N{\ren}yeah, that -that - -that's how we lost our cable guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.51,zh,,0,0,0,,那样的经历的确会令人深受打击\N{\ren}Anyways, that kind of experience shakes you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:06:00.69,zh,,0,0,0,,很抱歉误导你了，祝你一切顺利\N{\ren}So, sorry I misled you, have a nice life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.56,zh,,0,0,0,,尼克，你有访客\N{\ren}Nick. You got a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:11.31,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，你发生了什么事？\N{\ren}Damn, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.53,zh,,0,0,0,,这里的守卫喜欢在周日揍我们\N{\ren}The guards like to beat us on Sundays.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.96,zh,,0,0,0,,-还是比周一好 -天啊，周一会怎样？\N{\ren} -Still better than Mondays. -Geez, what happens then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.88,zh,,0,0,0,,他们会绑住我们，舔我们的脸\N{\ren}They lick our faces when we're tied down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.45,zh,,0,0,0,,而且那天会吃肉饼\N{\ren}Plus it's meat loaf day. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:21.23,zh,,0,0,0,,你可以离开了，兄弟\N{\ren}you're leaving now, buddy. Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.06,zh,,0,0,0,,是我刚刚从守卫身上偷到的\N{\ren}I -I swiped 'em off the guard on my way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:26.63,zh,,0,0,0,,我是说，好啊，我可以解开我的枷锁，然后呢？\N{\ren}I -I mean, sure, yeah, I could undo my lock, but then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.46,zh,,0,0,0,,在被全世界最聪明的人抛弃后\N{\ren}After the smartest guy in the world's done with ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:29.98,zh,,0,0,0,,我会很难找到立足之地的\N{\ren}it's kinda hard to find a footing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:31.42,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我才得救你出去\N{\ren}That's why I need to get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.11,zh,,0,0,0,,我们不是有问题的人，他才是\N{\ren}We're not the problem, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:37.94,zh,,0,0,0,,如果你能重新开始，或许我也能\N{\ren}And if you can have a fresh start, then maybe I can too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.25,zh,,0,0,0,,我们又不是要越狱\N{\ren}It's not like it's a prison break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.73,zh,,0,0,0,,只是要离开\N{\ren}We're just leaving, like, a hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.25,zh,,0,0,0,,特别积极帮你的医院\N{\ren}that wants to help you extra bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:45.73,zh,,0,0,0,,跟我走\N{\ren}Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.78,zh,,0,0,0,,快回来，快把门打开\N{\ren}Hey get back here, you better open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.26,zh,,0,0,0,,-我是真的会飞 -继续跑，尼克\N{\ren} -I canfly! -Keep running, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:55.48,zh,,0,0,0,,你流越多汗，脸颊就越咸\N{\ren}The more you sweat, the saltier your cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:57.27,zh,,0,0,0,,-你舔这个吧 -谢了，莫蒂\N{\ren} -Lick this! -Thanks, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.97,zh,,0,0,0,,他的舌头跟猫一样\N{\ren}That dude's got a tongue like a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:02.45,zh,,0,0,0,,拦住传送男孩\N{\ren}Stop those Portal Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:05.45,zh,,0,0,0,,听到没有？这称号不错\N{\ren}Did you hear that? That's gonna stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:07.58,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，就像成龙一样\N{\ren}Damn. Just like Jackie Chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.76,zh,,0,0,0,,那我就是克里斯塔克了\N{\ren}Hah! I guess that makes me Chris Tucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.41,zh,,0,0,0,,应该吧？\N{\ren}I -I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.81,zh,,0,0,0,,我来了\N{\ren}Gonna get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:25.51,zh,,0,0,0,,靠，你有看到吗？\N{\ren}Holy shit! Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.95,zh,,0,0,0,,你用呕吐物弄瞎了一个人\N{\ren}I mean you blinded a guy with puke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:28.17,zh,,0,0,0,,太酷了\N{\ren}Oh, it was insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.00,zh,,0,0,0,,-来击掌 -这样对吗？\N{\ren} -Gimme dap. -Am I doing it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:31.39,zh,,0,0,0,,这样算击掌吗？\N{\ren}D -D -Did I give you a dap yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.78,zh,,0,0,0,,看看我们，我们逃脱了\N{\ren}Look at us. We got out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:34.96,zh,,0,0,0,,我们逃离了疯人院和瑞克\N{\ren}And not just from the asylum but from Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.31,zh,,0,0,0,,你现在能自己定义什么是历险了\N{\ren}You get to say what an adventure is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.70,zh,,0,0,0,,那份清单还在吗？\N{\ren}You still got that list?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:40.35,zh,,0,0,0,,没有瑞克的科技就做不了那些事\N{\ren}Dude, we can't do that stuff without Rick's tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:45.49,zh,,0,0,0,,那传送男孩该搞到一把传送枪了\N{\ren}Then it's time the Portal Boys get themselves a portal gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:46.84,zh,,0,0,0,,别忘了之前的训练内容，乌鸦\N{\ren}Remember your training, crows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.88,zh,,0,0,0,,偶像应该就在转弯处\N{\ren}The idol should be around that corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:57.33,zh,,0,0,0,,你们是选择性遵守训练内容吗？\N{\ren}Do you guys just follow training when you feel like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.63,zh,,0,0,0,,这样不叫受过训练，叫随心所欲\N{\ren}That's not being trained, that's being dicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.86,zh,,0,0,0,,我懂了，真正的宝藏是同理心\N{\ren}Ah, now I see. The real treasure is empathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.07,zh,,0,0,0,,比任何摆饰都还要有价值\N{\ren}And that's worth way more than any knick -knack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:09.99,zh,,0,0,0,,你们可以再踏上另一趟历险了\N{\ren}You guys just earned yourselves another adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:11.52,zh,,0,0,0,,这次的历险是你们被开除了\N{\ren}The adventure is, you're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:13.52,zh,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我如果想变得有血有泪\N{\ren}Sorry, guys, if I wanted another bleeding heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:16.65,zh,,0,0,0,,我就会对真正的心脏注射复苏剂\N{\ren}I'd inject reanimator serum into an actual bleeding heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:18.35,zh,,0,0,0,,别担心，这颗行星\N{\ren}Relax, this is an avian planet
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.00,zh,,0,0,0,,有四千万种鸟\N{\ren}with 40 million species of bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.39,zh,,0,0,0,,跟我共事过一天\N{\ren}even one day of working under me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:23.40,zh,,0,0,0,,就会被当天才看\N{\ren}will make you apex geniuses down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:24.92,zh,,0,0,0,,快跳进1970年代的银行车道\N{\ren}Now hop into these pneumatic canisters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.62,zh,,0,0,0,,会用的气动管里\N{\ren}they used to use at bank drive -thrus in the '70s.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.59,zh,,0,0,0,,搞屁啊，是谁对我用牵引光束？\N{\ren}What the... Hey! Who's tractor beaming me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:40.59,zh,,0,0,0,,谁都别想对我用牵引光束\N{\ren}Nobody tractor beams me - -
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:43.90,zh,,0,0,0,,谁都别想反扰乱我的反牵引光…\N{\ren}Nobody descrambles my tractor beam scrambler to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.86,zh,,0,0,0,,抱歉对你用了牵引光束\N{\ren}Sorry for the tractor beaming,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:51.08,zh,,0,0,0,,但你是不是弄丢了这两只乌鸦？\N{\ren}but did you lose these two crows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:53.21,zh,,0,0,0,,不算是，是我放生它们的\N{\ren}Oh, uh, yeah, no I -I dropped 'em off 'cause
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.91,zh,,0,0,0,,因为我控制不了它们\N{\ren}I -I can't hold a candle to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.26,zh,,0,0,0,,感觉这样做才是对的\N{\ren}Y'know it s -seemed like a - -the decent thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.69,zh,,0,0,0,,成为乌鸦，训练自己\N{\ren}Be your crows. Train yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.30,zh,,0,0,0,,这样乌鸦就会受过训练\N{\ren}Crows are then trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.13,zh,,0,0,0,,我愿意接受你的提议\N{\ren}I'm open to what you're describing if it's easier
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.48,zh,,0,0,0,,因为我不想让我孙子太得意\N{\ren}than wiping an unearned smirk off my grandson's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:07.92,zh,,0,0,0,,-我该怎么做？ -看看你的乌鸦\N{\ren} -W -What do I do? -Look at your crows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.44,zh,,0,0,0,,成为你的乌鸦\N{\ren}Be your crows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:10.88,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，真庆幸我是灵长类\N{\ren}God I am so glad I'm a primate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.62,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，我在看乌鸦了\N{\ren}Fine. Looking at my crows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.88,zh,,0,0,0,,我们训练自己停止训练\N{\ren}We train ourselves to stop training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:19.41,zh,,0,0,0,,受过训练的人其实没受过训练，我们没受过训练\N{\ren}The trained are untrained, we are untrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.63,zh,,0,0,0,,所有训练都完成了\N{\ren}All training is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:23.89,zh,,0,0,0,,因为不需要任何训练\N{\ren}Because no training was needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:41.13,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，我懂了\N{\ren}My God. I -I get it, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:44.91,zh,,0,0,0,,我们能让莫蒂见识乌鸦的厉害了\N{\ren}We are gonna shove this crow shit down Morty's throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:46.61,zh,,0,0,0,,尼克，这样或许不太好\N{\ren}Nick, m -maybe this isn't a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.44,zh,,0,0,0,,我们如果被他抓到呢？\N{\ren}L -Like what if he catches us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.44,zh,,0,0,0,,-他可能会再把我困在母体里 -真是够了\N{\ren} -He could trap me in a Matrix again. -Listen to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:52.09,zh,,0,0,0,,我们会变这样\N{\ren}We wouldn't even be in this situation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:55.27,zh,,0,0,0,,都是因为被他恶搞\N{\ren}if the dude hadn't fucked us both over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:56.66,zh,,0,0,0,,该死，他一定是拿传送枪\N{\ren}Damn it. He must be showing the gun off
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.75,zh,,0,0,0,,向乌鸦炫耀了，真不公平\N{\ren}to his stupid crows - -i -it's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.76,zh,,0,0,0,,没关系，我们还是能拿其他东西\N{\ren}It's okay, we can still liberate all this other stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.76,zh,,0,0,0,,我们只拿需要的东西就好\N{\ren}Let's only grab what we need, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.45,zh,,0,0,0,,不，靠，这是瑞克的罐头压制器\N{\ren}Oh, no. Shit. That's Rick's can crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.11,zh,,0,0,0,,他花了三星期才做好\N{\ren}H -He spent three weeks perfecting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:10.11,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂老弟，你忘了我们是一伙的\N{\ren}Morty, buddy, you forget that we're in this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:12.85,zh,,0,0,0,,而且你是不是也觉得有点爽？\N{\ren}Besides, tell me that didn't feel the slightest bit good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.20,zh,,0,0,0,,是啊，但我们不能再搞破坏了\N{\ren}I mean yeah, but w -we can't do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.86,zh,,0,0,0,,为什么不能？\N{\ren}Why the hell not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.52,zh,,0,0,0,,来吧，婊子\N{\ren}Here we go, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.96,zh,,0,0,0,,儿子，你是不是跟陌生人结了盟\N{\ren}Son, have you fallen in with a weird stranger
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.87,zh,,0,0,0,,开始对外公的工作室搞破坏？\N{\ren}and are now trashing your grandpa's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.70,zh,,0,0,0,,我可以帮忙\N{\ren}'Cause I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:35.88,zh,,0,0,0,,爸？随便\N{\ren}Dad? Psh, whatever, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:37.97,zh,,0,0,0,,-好耶 -吃屎吧，瑞克\N{\ren} -Ah. Yeah! Yeah! -Now eat my ass, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:40.66,zh,,0,0,0,,去死吧，山查兹\N{\ren}Suck it, Sanchez!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:42.14,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，这就是那个东西吗？\N{\ren}Morty, is that what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.88,zh,,0,0,0,,这是很旧的机型\N{\ren}I mean, it's the equivalent of an iPhone 3
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:47.15,zh,,0,0,0,,而且还是空的，但传送男孩可以开始传送了\N{\ren}And it's empty but it means the Portal Boys be portal -ing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.54,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克快回来了\N{\ren}Rick incoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:49.98,zh,,0,0,0,,该死，我们得走了\N{\ren}Oh, crap, we better skedaddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.50,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂\N{\ren}Moooooorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.15,zh,,0,0,0,,我爸怎么办？他变成\N{\ren}But what about my dad, he -he's like a -a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.68,zh,,0,0,0,,-一滩水了 -车库都说了\N{\ren} -puddle. -You heard the garage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.33,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克回来之后会把他变回固体\N{\ren}Rick'll turn him back into a solid when he gets here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.90,zh,,0,0,0,,抱歉，爸，我得去当英雄了\N{\ren}Sorry, Dad, gotta go be heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.86,zh,,0,0,0,,车借我开，我爱你\N{\ren}G -Gonna take your car, love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.73,zh,,0,0,0,,就是屎色屋顶的那间\N{\ren}That's us down there with the poop brown roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:19.27,zh,,0,0,0,,-这是什么？ -这个吗？\N{\ren} -What is that? -Oh. Ha. That?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.75,zh,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\ren}T -That's...nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.75,zh,,0,0,0,,这里写着＂两只乌鸦＂，旁边是\N{\ren}But I see "Two Crows" written right here beside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:27.23,zh,,0,0,0,,＂猴脑基因＂＂半个保罗贾麦提＂，还有\N{\ren}Gene with donkey brains, half a Paul Giamatti, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.71,zh,,0,0,0,,＂情感狗屁＂\N{\ren}sentient shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:31.37,zh,,0,0,0,,意思是乌鸦很蠢吗？\N{\ren}I guess the "joke" being that crows are stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:33.19,zh,,0,0,0,,应该还有一些深层含意\N{\ren}I think it's a little more nuanced than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.63,zh,,0,0,0,,因为你才刚跟我们\N{\ren}Right, because you just learned
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.59,zh,,0,0,0,,学会同理心\N{\ren}empathy from us 10 minutes ago
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:39.07,zh,,0,0,0,,我们就该学习你们的幽默感吗？\N{\ren}but now we're going to learn we don't get your humor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.55,zh,,0,0,0,,真他妈狗屁\N{\ren}Fucking horse shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.42,zh,,0,0,0,,没错，根本没什么深层含意\N{\ren}Yeah, there's not a ton to "get," genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:45.73,zh,,0,0,0,,你想表达你孙子可以轻易被取代\N{\ren}the "joke" is your grandson was soreplaceable
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.30,zh,,0,0,0,,连两只乌鸦都能取代他\N{\ren}that "even" two crows could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.21,zh,,0,0,0,,是很好笑，但我们可笑不出来\N{\ren}Haha. It's funny except it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:52.91,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，说实话，我当时是这样想\N{\ren}Right, well, to be honest, that is how I felt at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:54.43,zh,,0,0,0,,但我改观了，\N{\ren}But I've -I've rounded a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.04,zh,,0,0,0,,是真的，各位\N{\ren}I seriously have, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:12:01.61,zh,,0,0,0,,已经来不及了，准备受死吧\N{\ren}Well, now it's time to round the corner of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:05.05,zh,,0,0,0,,乌鸦革命就此展开\N{\ren}Let the crow -volutionbegin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.40,zh,,0,0,0,,好可怕的声音，你做了什么？\N{\ren}Aw, that sound. What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:13.10,zh,,0,0,0,,我叫三百米内的乌鸦对付人类\N{\ren}Turned crows against dozens of humans in a 300 meter radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.58,zh,,0,0,0,,拜托帮帮忙\N{\ren}Heeeelllllp... pleaseee...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.59,zh,,0,0,0,,你在求情吗？\N{\ren}Oh, now you beg for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.41,zh,,0,0,0,,-不是我 -什么意思？\N{\ren} -That wasn't me. -What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.07,zh,,0,0,0,,救命，我在这里\N{\ren}Dooooown here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:21.90,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞，你他妈为什么是一滩水？\N{\ren}Jerry, what the fuck? Why are you a puddle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.81,zh,,0,0,0,,你配不上这两只乌鸦\N{\ren}You don't deserve these!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:25.25,zh,,0,0,0,,天才\N{\ren} -Haha. -Genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.81,zh,,0,0,0,,-你是不是在忙？ -对，杰瑞\N{\ren} -Caaatch you at a baaad time? -Yeah, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:29.64,zh,,0,0,0,,它们夺走了我的乌鸦\N{\ren}They took my goddamn crows!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:36.04,zh,,0,0,0,,别闹了，垃圾虫，快滚回洞里\N{\ren}Not now, Garbage Goober! Get back in your hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.65,zh,,0,0,0,,我们的第一场历险\N{\ren}Hohoho, our first adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.13,zh,,0,0,0,,就是这吗？\N{\ren}This definitely the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.79,zh,,0,0,0,,对，瑞克剥削他们很久了\N{\ren}Yeah, Rick's been ripping these guys off for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:47.14,zh,,0,0,0,,他们一定会很…\N{\ren}they'll -they'll be really - -
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:48.84,zh,,0,0,0,,感激\N{\ren}uh, grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:50.62,zh,,0,0,0,,-其实… -快搞到传送液吧\N{\ren}Y'know, there - -Let's just get that fluid, bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:54.58,zh,,0,0,0,,传送男孩马上就能开始传送了\N{\ren}The Portal Boys are about to be in portal business!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:57.67,zh,,0,0,0,,他在这里\N{\ren}Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.85,zh,,0,0,0,,这叛徒一直偷你们采的水晶\N{\ren}This rat was skimming your crystal harvest
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:03.33,zh,,0,0,0,,交给名叫瑞克山查兹的太空人\N{\ren}and sending it to a spaceman named Rick Sanchez.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.46,zh,,0,0,0,,-混蛋 -瑞克去死，踢他老二\N{\ren} -Bastard! -Screw Rick! Kick his dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:10.51,zh,,0,0,0,,对吧？但我和尼克阻止了这一切\N{\ren}Yeah, right?! But me and Nick here, we -we put a stop to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:12.99,zh,,0,0,0,,全昆塔克的人民都感谢你们\N{\ren}The people of Kuntak thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:14.47,zh,,0,0,0,,他是坏人，对吧？\N{\ren}He's a bad guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:15.95,zh,,0,0,0,,你们会好好惩罚他吧？\N{\ren}Y -You're gonna bring him to justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.82,zh,,0,0,0,,是，当然\N{\ren}Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:20.95,zh,,0,0,0,,好，合作愉快\N{\ren}Uh, okay, p -pleasure doing business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.48,zh,,0,0,0,,先等一下，莫蒂\N{\ren}Not so fast, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.39,zh,,0,0,0,,我们要拿到东西才能走\N{\ren}We're not leaving until we get what we came for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:25.87,zh,,0,0,0,,怪了，我正打算…\N{\ren}Funny, I'm prepared to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:28.18,zh,,0,0,0,,听着，我们想要传送液\N{\ren}So hey, look, wh -what we want is portal fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.83,zh,,0,0,0,,当作给我们的谢礼\N{\ren}As our thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:31.57,zh,,0,0,0,,传送液？\N{\ren}Portal fluid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.66,zh,,0,0,0,,我如果有传送液还会住在蜥蜴矿坑吗？\N{\ren}You think I'd live in a lizard mine if I had portal fluid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:38.49,zh,,0,0,0,,有道理，好吧，那我们只好大开杀戒了\N{\ren}Right, ok, or we could just kill you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.41,zh,,0,0,0,,他是开玩笑的，他…\N{\ren}He's kidding. He's - -t -the Portal Boys
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:42.76,zh,,0,0,0,,-传送男孩不会随便杀人 -只会杀怪兽\N{\ren}only kill with kindness.And with guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:46.33,zh,,0,0,0,,不，不，开枪的人不是我\N{\ren}Oh, no. Oh, no. I -I'm not the one shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:48.68,zh,,0,0,0,,-杀了他们 -抱歉\N{\ren} -Kill them! -I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:52.86,zh,,0,0,0,,住手，住手，他们没有武器\N{\ren}Stop! Stop! They're unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.21,zh,,0,0,0,,他妈搞什么？\N{\ren}Ahh! What the fuck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:56.86,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，莫蒂\N{\ren}Morty! Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:06.70,zh,,0,0,0,,你这基地真酷，很像《夜魔水晶》风格的成衣店\N{\ren}Cool place ya got here. Very Dark Crystal meets Hot Topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.35,zh,,0,0,0,,我的乌鸦呢？\N{\ren}Now where are my damn crows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.01,zh,,0,0,0,,搞什么？\N{\ren}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:15.40,zh,,0,0,0,,连这都是乌鸦主题？\N{\ren}Is there anything not on theme here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:28.72,zh,,0,0,0,,你们的灵长类还闯进了我们的船\N{\ren}Even now your primate storms our ship to assert his dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.42,zh,,0,0,0,,快来触碰圣蛋并变身\N{\ren}Touch the sacred egg and ascend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:34.42,zh,,0,0,0,,你们就不用再听命于那只怪兽了\N{\ren}No longer shall you take orders from this beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.20,zh,,0,0,0,,听命于你们就没关系吗？\N{\ren}But taking orders from you i -is fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:37.90,zh,,0,0,0,,闭嘴，猩猩\N{\ren}Silence, Ape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:42.38,zh,,0,0,0,,拜托，你们以为我的乌鸦会为了\N{\ren}C'mon, if you think my crows are gonna leave the great thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:44.91,zh,,0,0,0,,这些幻想狗屁抛下我们的关系？\N{\ren}we have for whatever high fantasy bullshit this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:47.91,zh,,0,0,0,,你们就错了，对吧，两位？\N{\ren}You 're wrong. R -Right, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.91,zh,,0,0,0,,这真的需要犹豫吗？\N{\ren}Th -This is seriously a toss -up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.57,zh,,0,0,0,,没人要接电话吗？\N{\ren}Uh...someone wanna get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:54.92,zh,,0,0,0,,是我的电话，对吧？\N{\ren}Oh. It's me, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:57.96,zh,,0,0,0,,我先看看是不是急事\N{\ren}Lemme just make sure it's not an emergency...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:15:00.58,zh,,0,0,0,,-你好 -瑞克，对不起，我闯大祸了\N{\ren}Yello. -Rick, I'm so sorry, I -I messed up big!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.80,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂？没关系，你不会比我惨\N{\ren}Morty? It's okay, y -ya can't be worse off than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.32,zh,,0,0,0,,我沾到了传送液，偷了你的东西\N{\ren}I -I got portal splashed, robbed you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.80,zh,,0,0,0,,找了个神经病当临时备胎\N{\ren}jumped into a rebound with a psycho,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.23,zh,,0,0,0,,还害死了一堆人\N{\ren}and -and left a trail of dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.50,zh,,0,0,0,,你还真忙碌\N{\ren}Wow, somebody's been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:09.93,zh,,0,0,0,,你选择那两只乌鸦\N{\ren}I -I did it 'cause you hurt my feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:11.28,zh,,0,0,0,,很伤我的心\N{\ren}w -when you chose the two crows!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.33,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，我只是在搞笑\N{\ren}Jesus, it was a bit, I'm getting my ass kicked
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.98,zh,,0,0,0,,我现在被这愚蠢的乌鸦情节害惨了，整个大翻车\N{\ren}by this dumb fucking crow story, it's all gone tits up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:19.42,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，我很想你\N{\ren}Ha, okay, I -I miss you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:22.12,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，我刚刚好像太诚实了\N{\ren}Uh, goddamn it, might've been a bit too frank there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.87,zh,,0,0,0,,我得晚点再回你电话了\N{\ren}Yeah... gonna have to call ya back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:35.09,zh,,0,0,0,,小手王八蛋\N{\ren}Tiny -handed little brat - -
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:37.61,zh,,0,0,0,,你以为恶搞我不用付出代价吗？\N{\ren}You think you can fuck with me and get away with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:48.01,zh,,0,0,0,,那你就不够了解尼克\N{\ren}Then you don't know Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:51.02,zh,,0,0,0,,被我抓到了，你根本不懂，对吧？\N{\ren}Busted. You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:52.80,zh,,0,0,0,,只要这传送口还在\N{\ren}As long as we have these portals,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:54.28,zh,,0,0,0,,你就永远逃不过我\N{\ren}you can never escape me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.67,zh,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\N{\ren}What the hell, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.28,zh,,0,0,0,,我们明明都是被瑞克虐待过的人\N{\ren}I -I thought we were both victims of Rick's abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.81,zh,,0,0,0,,或许是，或许不是\N{\ren}Maybe we are, maybe we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.55,zh,,0,0,0,,或许我们只是在同一间酒吧喝酒\N{\ren}Maybe we both just drink at the same bar
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:03.29,zh,,0,0,0,,我某天想拿走他的传送枪\N{\ren}and maybe one night I tried to take his portal gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.73,zh,,0,0,0,,我原本以为瑞克能让我出人头地\N{\ren}See I thought Rick was my ticket to something special,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:07.73,zh,,0,0,0,,结果其实是你，莫蒂\N{\ren}but it turns out you were, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:10.91,zh,,0,0,0,,看看我，我现在是传送男孩了\N{\ren}And look at me now - -I'm a Portal Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:13.39,zh,,0,0,0,,这名字烂透了，我只是配合而已\N{\ren}That name sucks! I was just trying to yes -and!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:16.04,zh,,0,0,0,,你不懂，莫蒂\N{\ren}You don't get it, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.57,zh,,0,0,0,,我们是搭档\N{\ren}We're partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:19.83,zh,,0,0,0,,快听话，否则我就让你生不如死\N{\ren}Now fall in line or I'll make your life a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:22.31,zh,,0,0,0,,不用，谢谢\N{\ren}No...thank...you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:25.53,zh,,0,0,0,,真可惜，你如果不跟我同一阵线，你就不能继续跟我相连\N{\ren}Pity, I can't have you connected to me if you're not on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.49,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我得杀了你\N{\ren}That means I gotta kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:29.66,zh,,0,0,0,,但是我已经有搭档了\N{\ren}The thing is, I already got a partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:31.93,zh,,0,0,0,,你没有升迁的空间\N{\ren}and there's no room for promotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:36.76,zh,,0,0,0,,你他妈做了什么？\N{\ren}What the fuck did you just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.80,zh,,0,0,0,,我要跟你彻底断干净\N{\ren}Cut you out of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:57.56,zh,,0,0,0,,你看你的盟友多快就抛下你了，瑞克山查兹？\N{\ren}See how quickly your allies abandon you, Rick Sanchez?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:17:00.22,zh,,0,0,0,,幸好抛弃是我的专业强项\N{\ren}Lucky for me, abandonment's my bread and butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.57,zh,,0,0,0,,靠，你应该要死的\N{\ren}Oh, shit. You were supposed to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.05,zh,,0,0,0,,不得不说\N{\ren}I gotta hand it to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:10.88,zh,,0,0,0,,是我多虑了，乌鸦科技真厉害\N{\ren}I was iffy about this one but crow tech slaps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:17.06,zh,,0,0,0,,快杀了他，蠢蛋\N{\ren}Finish him, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.41,zh,,0,0,0,,快动手吧\N{\ren}Go ahead. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.89,zh,,0,0,0,,你们太酷了\N{\ren}You guys look so rad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.80,zh,,0,0,0,,我甘愿被你们杀死\N{\ren}I deserve to go out this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:31.55,zh,,0,0,0,,-安眠酮 -安眠酮 -没问题\N{\ren}Bird...qua...luudes.Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:37.08,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，太棒了\N{\ren}Oh, my god, that was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.82,zh,,0,0,0,,你们刚刚明明能杀我\N{\ren}Y -You could've killed me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:41.30,zh,,0,0,0,,你们怎么会原谅我？\N{\ren}H -How did you guys ever forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.74,zh,,0,0,0,,没错，我们的关系\N{\ren}Right, 'cause this toxic thing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:44.57,zh,,0,0,0,,不受我和莫蒂的危险关系所定义\N{\ren}I have with Morty doesn't define us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:49.40,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，乌鸦真的超有同理心的\N{\ren}Man, crows are empathetic as fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:51.18,zh,,0,0,0,,这我一定要留着用\N{\ren}Definitely saving this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.45,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克和两只乌鸦\N{\ren}Rick and two crows!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.23,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，莫蒂\N{\ren}Oh, my god, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.58,zh,,0,0,0,,来，外公帮你治疗\N{\ren}Here, here come here l -let -let grandpa fix you up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:05.80,zh,,0,0,0,,你要机器手还是蜥蜴手？\N{\ren}What do you want, a robot hand? A lizard hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.41,zh,,0,0,0,,还是像上次那样的大手？\N{\ren}I can make it big again like that one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.76,zh,,0,0,0,,我的正常手就好\N{\ren}Just my regular hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:11.11,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，你现在没心情，我懂\N{\ren}Right, not a time for bits, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:15.42,zh,,0,0,0,,好了，焕然一新\N{\ren}There ya go, good as new.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:17.77,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我们和好了，对吧？\N{\ren}So we're like, back -back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.17,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克和莫蒂又合体了\N{\ren}Rick and Morty, together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:21.95,zh,,0,0,0,,完全重置吗？\N{\ren}Fu -Full reset? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.52,zh,,0,0,0,,不，莫蒂，我们就到此为止吧\N{\ren}No, Morty, I think we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.43,zh,,0,0,0,,因为我洒了传送液没告诉你吗？\N{\ren}Be -Because I spilled the portal fluid and didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:27.96,zh,,0,0,0,,不，莫蒂，是因为你不敢告诉我\N{\ren}No, Morty. 'Cause you were too afraid to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.78,zh,,0,0,0,,我们之间存在凌虐关系，懂吗？\N{\ren}What we had was abusive. Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.44,zh,,0,0,0,,我是坏搭档，因为我从没让你成为真正的搭档\N{\ren}I'm a bad partner because I never made you a true partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.05,zh,,0,0,0,,乌鸦让我认清了这点\N{\ren}The crows made me see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.83,zh,,0,0,0,,我原本以为它们跟你一样可笑\N{\ren}I thought they were a joke like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.62,zh,,0,0,0,,但它们其实比我们都还要有智慧\N{\ren}but it turns out they're more enlightened than any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.97,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，那它们有什么优势？\N{\ren}O -Okay? And -And what's the undercut?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.62,zh,,0,0,0,,你没听懂\N{\ren}You're not hearing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.84,zh,,0,0,0,,我已经彻底改变了，我得跟着乌鸦离开\N{\ren}I will never be the same so I need to leave with the crows
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.63,zh,,0,0,0,,看看它们还能教会我什么\N{\ren}and see what more they can teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:51.98,zh,,0,0,0,,来，这给你\N{\ren}Here, I want you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:54.29,zh,,0,0,0,,我…\N{\ren}Oh, wow I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:57.46,zh,,0,0,0,,知道吗，瑞克？你真的变了\N{\ren}You know what, Rick? You really have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:19:00.47,zh,,0,0,0,,谢了，莫蒂\N{\ren}Thanks, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.30,zh,,0,0,0,,我永远都会是你的外公，莫蒂\N{\ren}I'll always be your grandpa, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.78,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是变得很着迷于乌鸦\N{\ren}Just kinda obsessed with crows now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.11,zh,,0,0,0,,靠，瑞克和两只乌鸦\N{\ren}Aww shit! Rick and two crows!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:37.55,zh,,0,0,0,,这是我的新系列\N{\ren}Kicking off my new franchise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:39.20,zh,,0,0,0,,整个星系都是我们的电话线\N{\ren}The galaxy is our telephone wire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.38,zh,,0,0,0,,我们可以拍一千季\N{\ren}We'll do a thousand seasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:42.77,zh,,0,0,0,,每季14集，每集9秒\N{\ren}14 episodes each, 9 -9 seconds a pop
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:44.25,zh,,0,0,0,,因为这就是电视的未来\N{\ren}because that's the future of viewing - -
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:46.21,zh,,0,0,0,,在鞋子上看节目，真狡猾\N{\ren}shows on your shoes - -Sneaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.51,zh,,0,0,0,,趁大家在穿鞋子的时候\N{\ren}That's when you've got everybody's attention - -
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.04,zh,,0,0,0,,引起他们的注意\N{\ren}when they're putting crap on their feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.74,zh,,0,0,0,,让他们想笑、想哭\N{\ren}That's when they wanna laugh. Cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:53.04,zh,,0,0,0,,感受到除了穿鞋感之外的东西\N{\ren}Or feel anything besides a shoe going on their foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.70,zh,,0,0,0,,在鞋子上看情境喜剧\N{\ren}Watch sitcoms on your sneakers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:56.26,zh,,0,0,0,,《瑞克和两只乌鸦秀》\N{\ren}The Rick and Two Crows Show,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.35,zh,,0,0,0,,我们会在路上放核桃\N{\ren}we're gonna be layin' - -layin' walnuts on the road
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:01.22,zh,,0,0,0,,让车轮把核桃压开，懂我的意思吗？\N{\ren}for car tires to open em' you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:05.23,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克和两只乌鸦直到永远\N{\ren}Forever, it's Rick and two crows, forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:42.74,zh,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里？\N{\ren}Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:44.31,zh,,0,0,0,,你知道的\N{\ren}Oh, well, ya know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:46.18,zh,,0,0,0,,红灯亮起通常就代表有\N{\ren}the -the red light usually means there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:47.57,zh,,0,0,0,,垃圾\N{\ren}garbage...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.32,zh,,0,0,0,,你是真的还没跟瑞克谈过吗？\N{\ren}Did you seriously not talk to Rick yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:50.62,zh,,0,0,0,,我有稍微暗示过\N{\ren}I kinda hinted at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:52.10,zh,,0,0,0,,我知道我不是来吃垃圾的\N{\ren}L -Look, I know it's not the job
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.15,zh,,0,0,0,,但这也是很正当的工作\N{\ren}I came here for but it's an honest living.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:55.45,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，哈罗\N{\ren}Goddamn it, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.58,zh,,0,0,0,,他们都叫你＂垃圾虫＂吗？\N{\ren}What do they call you - -Garbage Goober?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:59.59,zh,,0,0,0,,你明明就是医生\N{\ren}You are a doctor for god sakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:01.33,zh,,0,0,0,,我也不知道怎么会变成这样\N{\ren}Look, I don't know how I let this happen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:04.81,zh,,0,0,0,,但我现在已经没办法回头了\N{\ren}but I -I've let it play out so long that I can't stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:07.59,zh,,0,0,0,,你太懦弱了\N{\ren}You're a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.94,zh,,0,0,0,,没错，一切就到此为止\N{\ren}You're right. This ends here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:12.60,zh,,0,0,0,,垃圾虫，来吃新鲜的垃圾吧\N{\ren}Garbage Goober, we got freshy trash trash for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:16.82,zh,,0,0,0,,这次的特别臭，你一定会喜欢\N{\ren}Extra stinky just the way you like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.95,zh,,0,0,0,,垃圾，我好爱垃圾\N{\ren}Mmm, trash, I love trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:21.57,zh,,0,0,0,,好吃的垃圾，我想吃垃圾\N{\ren}yum yum trash, I wanna eat trash.
